comments: She made a boring topic (communism) actually interesting. My writing skills really improved from taking this class.
Wonderful professor. Interesting, funny, and extremely helpful. I learned so much about writing that I never knew. I wish I could have her again!

She is a very good teacher who takes a personal interest in all her students. However, the pro-communist agenda she pushes throughout her class is almost unbearable. In her favor she does grade fairly even if you take an opposing stance.
A helpful and caring instructor. Not only did I learn a lot in this course, but it made me appreciate reading and writing more.
